data.value: The most important ingredients that give the taste to Ali Nazik kebab cooked using carrot meat or minced meat can be listed as eggplant and yoghurt. Roasted eggplant, garlic, yogurt and meat with a great taste and appearance of the palate and the minds of this unique kebab that leaves a pleasant taste, among the most popular dishes of the country.
